question:
Ğ’ $\triangle{RST}$, Ğ¿Ğ¾ĞºĞ°Ğ·Ğ°Ğ½, $\sin{R}=\frac{2}{5}$. ĞšĞ°ĞºĞ²Ğ¾ Ğµ $\sin{T}$?

[asy]
pair R,S,T;
T = (0,0);
S = (2,0);
R = (2,sqrt(21));
draw(R--S--T--R);
draw(rightanglemark(R,S,T,10));
